Adding Year Slicer 17
Adding Year Slicer 


1.From the Visualization pane, click on Slicer and Drag ‘Year’ column from Power Plant table to the Values field of Slice 
2.In the Format Pane on the right, Go to General => Properties and enter the values below for formatting
General=>
Height = 92
Width = 215
Position => 
Horizontal = 0
Vertical = 81
Title => on
Title->Text = Year
Font = Segoe UI Bold, Size = 12
Text Color = #FFFFFF
Background Color = #A38600
Horizontal Alignment -> Center
Effects=>
Background = On
Color = #F8F6EB
Transparency = 0%
Visual =>
Style -> Slicer Setting -> Between
Slicer Header -> On
Text = Year
Font = DIN – 12
Font Color = #252423
Boarder Color = #605E5C
Line Width = 1
Values =>
Font = Segoe UI Bold – 9
Font Color = #000000
Slider = On
